Class ListObj<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ListObj<T>

  • public class ListObj<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class of Generic Linked List ListObj. ListObj is a dynamic list that record first and last element reference. Elements T can be added and removed from list.
    Version:
    24 April 2018
    Author:
    Rahmat Nur Ibrahim Santosa/13516009
